de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.components.processor.runtime
Class TmqlRuntimeImpl

java.lang.Object
  de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.components.processor.runtime.TmqlRuntimeImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
ITMQLRuntime
Direct Known Subclasses:
TmqlRuntime, TmqlRuntime2007
public abstract class TmqlRuntimeImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITMQLRuntime

Core component of the processing model of the TMQL4J engine. The runtime encapsulate the whole TMQL process chain and store internal states and results. An instance of TmqlRuntimeImpl is used as public interface to Java applications using the TMQL engine.

Author:
Sven Krosse

run

public IQuery run(org.tmapi.core.TopicMap topicMap,
                  java.lang.String query)
           throws TMQLRuntimeException
Execution method of the TMQL runtime.

Method starts the execution of the encapsulated processing chain and store the total execution time.

The runtime will be create a IQuery representation by calling QueryFactory#buildQuery(String) and transform the given query to a TMQL query.

Specified by:
run in interface ITMQLRuntime
Parameters:
topicMap - the topicMap
query - the query to execute
Returns:
the create query
